<p>
	This bright yellow candle with red hearts on the surface has a beautiful citrus, sweet fragrance. &nbsp;Its exciting citrus mixture utilises zesty lemon, sweet orange and tart lime alongside notes of buttery vanilla and creamy caramel. The candle has been blended with quality lemon and lime essential oils and burns for approximately 45 hours.&nbsp; When in use place the candle tin on a heat resistant surface. Ensure the candle is kept away from any flammable materials and do not move the candle while alight or while the wax is molten. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Do not leave a burning candle unattended. This candle is suitable for vegans.</p>
